    notes (c), (g) and (j).

Created 1.4.1955 out of the parishes of Wellow, Camerton and 
    Dunkerton. See also Table 2, note (j).

    also Table 2, note (c).

Created 1.4.1955 out of the parish of Wellow. See also Table 2, 
    note (j).

Abolished 1.4.1953 and divided between the parishes of Charlcombe 
    and Kelston. See also Table 2, notes (a) and (d).
